        },
        "description": "Represents a request to enable or disable whether Amazon SES forwards you bounce and complaint notifications through email. For information about email feedback forwarding, see the <a href=\"https://docs.aws.amazon.com/ses/latest/DeveloperGuide/notifications-via-email.html\">Amazon SES Developer Guide</a>."
