                "description": "The custom MAIL FROM domain that you want the verified identity to use. The MAIL FROM domain must 1) be a subdomain of the verified identity, 2) not be used in a \"From\" address if the MAIL FROM domain is the destination of email feedback forwarding (for more information, see the <a href=\"https://docs.aws.amazon.com/ses/latest/DeveloperGuide/mail-from.html\">Amazon SES Developer Guide</a>), and 3) not be used to receive emails. A value of <code>null</code> disables the custom MAIL FROM setting for the identity."
